snippet.title: A Building Full of Cats (Trailer)
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1969080/A_Building_Full_of_Cats/
A Building Full of Cats is a hidden object game where you need to pet all the cats in the building. Don't leave any cat behind!
